OL,6,FCampaigners hope the farm where Robert
OL,7,FBurns wrote Auld Lang Syne can be
OL,8,Fsaved with an international
OL,9,Ffundraising appeal seeking to raise
OL,10,F#12 million.
OL,12,FScotland's bard built Ellisland Farm,
OL,13,Fnear Dumfries, in Dumfries and
OL,14,FGalloway, himself aged 29, as a home
OL,15,Ffor his wife and children.
