OL,4,C'to be restored if #12m can be raised'
OL,6,FThe Category A-listed building was
OL,7,Fbuilt in 1788, and Burns wrote many of
OL,8,Fhis most noted poems there including
OL,9,FTam O Shanter, and My Heart's In The
OL,10,FHighlands, but in recent years it has
OL,11,Fsuffered from damp, decay and
OL,12,Fstructural deterioration.
OL,14,FThe Robert Burns Ellisland Trust
OL,15,Fformed in 2020 to save the site and
OL,16,Fhas recreated it in Minecraft,
OL,17,Fgenerated revenue with holiday
OL,18,Faccommodation and restored the Burns
OL,19,FFamily Flute so it can be played after
OL,20,Fcenturies.
