OL,4,C'to be restored if #12m can be raised'
OL,6,FThe Robert Burns Ellisland Trust's
OL,7,Frestoration plans will recreate the
OL,8,Ffarmhouse, drawing on newly discovered
OL,9,Fmaterial including the Barnbougle
OL,10,FPapers, shopping lists from 1788
OL,11,Fdetailing everything from furniture
OL,12,Fand floorboards to seeds for the
OL,13,Fkitchen garden.
OL,15,FThe project will also establish an
OL,16,Fenvironmentally controlled museum
OL,17,Fspace for the collection, and enhance
OL,18,Fthe landscape's biodiversity.
