OL,6,FThe Trust is launching its
OL,7,Finternational fundraising campaign on
OL,8,FFriday at an event in Glasgow, just
OL,9,Fahead of St Andrew's Day, at the
OL,10,Fstudio of Collective Architecture
OL,11,Fwhich is currently working on plans to
OL,12,Frestore the site, with completed
OL,13,Fdesigns due to be revealed in early
OL,14,F2026.
