OL,6,FThe launch event will feature the
OL,7,Fpremiere of a specially commissioned
OL,8,Ffilm featuring Scotland's national
OL,9,FMakar, Peter Mackay, and the former
OL,10,Fpoet laureate of Jamaica, Lorna
OL,11,FGoodison, who recently completed a
OL,12,FScottish Poetry Library residency at
OL,13,FEllisland.
OL,15,FFrancis Hutcheson, Professor of
OL,16,FScottish Literature at the University
OL,17,Fof Glasgow ` and one of the world's
OL,18,Fleading Burns scholars, will speak at
OL,19,Fthe event.
