OL,6,FThe flute which was restored will also
OL,7,Fbe played after the screening, along
OL,8,Fwith a performance from singer Robyn
OL,9,FStapleton.
OL,11,FDuncan Dornan, chair of the Robert
OL,12,FBurns Ellisland Trust and current
OL,13,Fchair of Museums Galleries Scotland,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Tonight marks the beginning of
OL,15,Fan ambitious campaign to secure the
OL,16,Ffuture of a site of international
OL,17,Fcultural significance. Having led the
OL,18,FBurrell Renaissance, I know what can
OL,19,Fbe achieved when vision meets
OL,20,Fdetermination and commitment.
