OL,6,F"Ellisland has that same potential to
OL,7,Fbecome both a national landmark and a
OL,8,Fsource of enduring inspiration. This
OL,9,Fis our opportunity to preserve the
OL,10,Fhome where the world's most famous
OL,11,Fsong was born and ensure it thrives
OL,12,Ffor generations to come."
OL,14,FJoan McAlpine, former MSP for South
OL,15,FScotland, has led the development of
OL,16,FEllisland as project director since
OL,17,F2021.
