OL,6,FMs McAlpine said: "This campaign is
OL,7,Fabout reconnecting people with the
OL,8,Flandscape and creativity that shaped
OL,9,FBurns's greatest works.
OL,11,F"Over the past few years, we've
OL,12,Fundertaken extensive research and
OL,13,Fconsultation to understand what
OL,14,FEllisland needs structurally, and to
OL,15,Fexplore what it could become.
OL,17,F"It quickly became clear that we had
OL,18,Fto find a way to also make the site
OL,19,Fsustainable ` generating income to
OL,20,Fsupport the heritage and culture.
