OL,6,F"This site has immense potential as
OL,7,Fboth a cultural destination and an
OL,8,Fengine for regional economic
OL,9,Fregeneration.
OL,11,F"We're building a place where today's
OL,12,Fartists and musicians can find
OL,13,Finspiration in the same surroundings
OL,14,Fthat gave us Auld Lang Syne, while
OL,15,Fcreating sustainable opportunities for
OL,16,Four local community and visitors from
OL,17,Faround the world."
