OL,6,FA key aspect of the project is the
OL,7,Fcreation of visitor accommodation
OL,8,Fbased on The Hermitage, a tiny
OL,9,Fsummerhouse in the neighbouring Friars
OL,10,FCarse estate where Burns would write
OL,11,Fin peace among nature, and the project
OL,12,Fwill create "hermitages", scattered
OL,13,Facross the 140-acre estate, where
OL,14,Fartists and writers can work, but
OL,15,Fwhich will also provide income.
